    "headline": "Akamai Technologies forecasts quarterly results below expectations",
    "summary": "Akamai Technologies forecast second-quarter profit and revenue below Wall ‌Street expectations on Thursday, as the ‌company navigates a challenging macroeconomic environment marked by ​high memory costs and cautious enterprise spending. A sharp rise in the cost of memory infrastructure has rippled across the technology ‌industry, as enterprises ⁠such as Akamai prepare to spend more to secure the ⁠crucial hardware. Investors have also been concerned about the impact of new agentic security tools ​from companies ​such as ​Anthropic on traditional security ‌technology.",
